---
import interactiveM from '@assets/mobile/image-interactive.jpg';
import interactiveD from '@assets/desktop/image-interactive.jpg';
---


<section id="feature">
    <div class="section-container">
        <div class="relative flex flex-col max-w-6xl mx-auto my-24  text-darkGray md:flex-row md:px-0">
            <img src={interactiveM} alt="" class="lg:hidden"/>

            <img src={interactiveD} alt="" class="hidden lg:block"/>
            <div class="top-48 pr-0 bg-white md:absolute md:right-0 md:py-20 md:pl-20">
                <h2 class="max-w-lg mt-10 md:mt-0 mb-6 font-sans text-3xl md:text-5xl text-center md:text-left text-veryDarkGray uppercase ">the leader in interactive vr</h2>
                <p class="max-w-[279px] mx-auto text-center font-alata text-[15px]">
                    Founded in 2011, Loopstudios has been producing world-class virtual reality projects for some of the best companies around the globe. Our award-winning creations have transformed businesses through digital experiences that bind to their brand.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

